{"pageProps":{"data":{"news_id":"600","news_catgory":"1","hot_news":"0","news_push":"","news_on_top":"1","news_title":"勞力短缺增加底氣 愈來愈多日本勞工勇於抗議職場不公","news_summary":"","image_path":"","news_des":null,"news_content":"<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;&#10;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>2019-12-26 11:01 </span><span style='mso-bidi-font-size:&#10;12.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>經濟日報 編譯黃淑玲／綜合外電</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>金融時報說，日本勞力短缺的現實提升了勞工話語權，這可由今年以來幾波勞工勇於發聲抗議職場霸凌的事件，看出這個趨勢。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>日本職場向來對女性職員有著許多不成文規定，像是上班必須化妝、穿高跟鞋、視力需要矯正者甚至不能戴一般眼鏡必須戴隱形眼鏡。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>在殯葬禮儀公司擔任兼職助理的石川優實，今年初在社群媒體上仿效西方抗議職場性騷擾的<span lang='EN-US'>#MeToo</span>活動，發起拒穿高跟鞋的<span lang='EN-US'>#KuToo</span>網路連署運動（<span lang='EN-US'>Ku</span>同時是日語鞋子與疼痛的字首發音）時，支持的回應從全日本蜂擁而來。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>金融時報指出，<span lang='EN-US'>#KuToo</span>運動得到的熱烈回響，反映出社會對性別平等的關切，以及在職場被霸凌的員工站出來為自己的權益發聲的意願正在增強。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>根據政府勞工機構的統計，到機構諮商雇主霸凌或濫權的個案，過去十年間增加一倍以上，由<span lang='EN-US'>2009</span>年的<span lang='EN-US'>35,759</span>件增加到今年的<span lang='EN-US'>82,797</span>件。勞工政策與訓練研究所資深研究員<span lang='EN-US'>Masato Gunji</span>說：「現今勞動人力短缺無疑是促使這種改變的部分原因。」</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>明年將上路的工作型態改革法案，是日本職場環境變化最顯著的體現，這項新法為防範勞工過勞工作，規定加班時數全年不得超過<span lang='EN-US'>720</span>小時。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>另外，日本兼職勞工加入工會的比率也由<span lang='EN-US'>2013</span>年的<span lang='EN-US'>6.7%</span>提高到去年的<span lang='EN-US'>8.1%</span>。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;<img alt='' src='/user_files/news_files/%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC(1).jpg' style='width: 800px; height: 533px;' /></span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>日本勞動市場出現良性改變。 美聯社</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;&#10;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>資料來源：<span lang='EN-US'>https://udn.com/news/story/6809/4249950</span></span></span></p>\n","keyword":"","news_order_id":"0","create_date":"2019-12-30","clk_count":"159"}},"__N_SSG":true}